#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "About {NAME_APP}"
msgstr "About {NAME_APP}"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "Welcome to {NAME_APP} – your mobile companion for stylists, makeup artists, and other professionals! This app is designed to help you efficiently manage client meetings, take notes, and sync your schedule with your phone's calendar."
msgstr "Welcome to {NAME_APP} – your mobile companion for stylists, makeup artists, and other professionals! This app is designed to help you efficiently manage client meetings, take notes, and sync your schedule with your phone's calendar."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "Key features of the app:"
msgstr "Key features of the app:"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "Clients and Notes: Easily create and store client profiles, take notes for each meeting."
msgstr "Clients and Notes: Easily create and store client profiles, take notes for each meeting."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "Calendar Sync: Your meetings automatically sync with your device's calendar."
msgstr "Calendar Sync: Your meetings automatically sync with your device's calendar."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "Reminders: Receive notifications for upcoming meetings and send SMS reminders to clients."
msgstr "Reminders: Receive notifications for upcoming meetings and send SMS reminders to clients."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "Ease of Use: Intuitive interface for quick access to your data."
msgstr "Ease of Use: Intuitive interface for quick access to your data."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "Subscriptions: Access additional features with a subscription, including a free trial period."
msgstr "Subscriptions: Access additional features with a subscription, including a free trial period."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "We are always striving to improve our app to make it even more useful for you. Therefore, we appreciate your feedback and suggestions for enhancement. Together, we can take {NAME_APP} to the next level!"
msgstr "We are always striving to improve our app to make it even more useful for you. Therefore, we appreciate your feedback and suggestions for enhancement. Together, we can take {NAME_APP} to the next level!"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "Thank you for choosing {NAME_APP}!"
msgstr "Thank you for choosing {NAME_APP}!"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "How to delete personal data?"
msgstr "How to delete personal data?"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
msgid "If you wish to have your personal data deleted from the {NAME_APP} mobile application and website, you need to access the application, proceed to your profile, then go to the profile settings. At the top left corner, you will find the \"Delete\" button. After pressing it, your account will be deleted along with all your publications. Then, you will be redirected to the \"Welcome\" page where you can register again."
msgstr "If you wish to have your personal data deleted from the {NAME_APP} mobile application and website, you need to access the application, proceed to your profile, then go to the profile settings. At the top left corner, you will find the \"Delete\" button. After pressing it, your account will be deleted along with all your publications. Then, you will be redirected to the \"Welcome\" page where you can register again."

